    dc:title "The Herniosina story continues in the Mediterranean: H. calabra sp. nov. from Calabria and H. erymantha Rohacek, new female from the Peloponnese (Diptera, Sphaeroceridae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures3-7>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures8-13>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figure14>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures15-20>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures33-41>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures42-44>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys..72235.figures21-22> ;
